Seven Killed as Burkina Faso Military Crush Mutiny by Soldiers at Base

-- B y   S i m o n   G o n g o
-- 
2011-06-05T06:16:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-05/seven-killed-as-burkina-faso-military-crush-mutiny-by-soldiers-at-base.html
Six soldiers and one girl were killed
in Bobo Dioulasso,  Burkina Faso , during a military operation to
crush a mutiny in an army base, Safety Minister Jerome Bougouma
said.  Twenty-five civilians and eight military personnel were
also injured, while 57 soldiers arrested, he said yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Simon Gongo in Ouagadougou at 
 sgongo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
